Title: Breezy
Writer: Pendleton Ward (creator), Jesse Moynihan, Derek Ballard, Kent Osborne (story), Pendleton Ward (story), Jack Pendarvis (story), Adam Muto (story)
Actors: Maria Bamford, Ashly Burch, John DiMaggio, Melinda Hill
Plot: In an attempt to help his wilting arm-flower, Finn begins a search for smooches with the help of a friendly bee named Breezy.
